 kitchen in your home. They are available in a range of selected colors or in RAL Classic shades on request, combined with fine metallic finishes.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><ul style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><li>2 x 175W infrared lights for wall-mounted food warmers (one light for mod. UAM76)</li><li>Front LED bar</li><li>Painted steel body, AISI 304 stainless steel (only inox version)</li><li>Anodised aluminium filters</li><li>Automatic filter cleaning warning light</li><li>Maximum air flow 600 cfm</li><li>Maximum power 705 W (UAM-76 535 W)</li><li>3 speeds + intensive</li><li>Flue outlet hole 5\\u2033 7/8</li><li>Automatic delayed shutdown</li></ul><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Limited 2 Year Parts and Labor Warranty</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>California Proposition 65</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">WARNING: Cancer and Reproductive Harm</p><p><a href=\\\"http://www.P65Warnings.ca.gov\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">www.P65Warnings.ca.gov</a></p></div>.<br><br><strong>Freight Charges May Apply</strong><br><br></div>      </div>      <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" data-slug=\\\"accessories\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Accessories</span> </span></h3>      <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\">         <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\">                     </div>      </div>      <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_videos\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tab