"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"Stainless Steel\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Exterior Width\", \"Option2 Value\": \"30\\\"\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - Majestic II Wall Mount Hoods - UAM150BU\", \"Variant Inventory Tracker\": \"shopify\", \"Variant Inventory Qty\": \"10\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UAM150BU\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/UAM150BU_p16489-1.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/UAM150BU_p16489-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UAM150BU_p16489_174230.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/UAM150BU_p16489_4509-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/UAM150BU_p16489_4510-1.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"3840.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202343398\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \"      <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\">         <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"product-desc\\\"><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Majestic Hoods</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">A fusion of beauty and functionality, Majestic is a bold, masterful embodiment of the ultimate complete system top performing range cookers and hoods in the kitchen. A statement-piece that blends into every setting and immediately takes center stage, with a style featuring rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, solutions and technologies deriving directly from the world of professional cooking.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Majestic hoods are the perfect companion of your range cookers, that decorate the home thanks to their rounded shapes forged in pure steel with painstakingly made details.\\u00a0</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">They are true gems of professionalism, designed for the kitchen in your home. They are available in a range of selected colors or in RAL Classic shades on request, combined with fine metallic finishes.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><ul style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><li>2 x 175W infrared lights for wall-mounted food warmers (one light for mod. UAM76)</li><li>Front LED bar</li><li>Painted steel body, AISI 304 stainless steel (only inox version)</li><li>Anodised aluminium filters</li><li>Automatic filter cleaning warning light</li><li>Maximum air flow 850 cfm on models UAM120 \\u2013 UAM150</li><li>Maximum power 705 W (UAM-76 535 W)</li><li>3 speeds + intensive</li><li>Flue outlet hole 7\\u2033 7/8 on models UAM120 \\u2013 UAM150</li><li>Automatic delayed shutdown</li></ul><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>California Proposition 65</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">WARNING: Cancer and Reproductive Harm</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong><a href=\\\"http://www.P65Warnings.ca.gov\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: normal\\\">www.P65Warnings.ca.gov</span></a></strong></p></div>.<br><br><strong>Freight Charges May Apply</strong><br><br></div>      </div>      <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" data-slug=\\\"accessories\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Accessories</span> </span></h3>      <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\">         <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\">                     </div>      </div>      <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span 